Package energy.usef.core.service.helper

Helper classes for the transport core.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NotificationHelperService
    Failed message notification hook.
    WorkItemExecution
    This interface is used to pass along trigger implementations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTriggerRegisterHelperService
    Helper service class to register a new trigger in the SchedulerHelperService.
    DispatcherHelperService
    This service is designed to route incoming XML messages to corresponding controllers for processing.
    JMSHelperService
    JMS Service.
    KeystoreHelperService
    Utility class to interact with the application Keystore.
    MessageMetadataBuilder
    Builder class for the building a new MessageMetadata.
    OutgoingErrorMessageDispatcherHelperService
    This service is designed to route outgoing error XML messages to corresponding controllers for processing.
    SchedulerHelperService
    Helper service class to register scheduled call to methods.
    WorkItem
    Helper class used for scheduling Runnable classes.
